1. Design a VI to display the previous and current values of a continuously changing
signal using feedback node.
    current: 239            previous: 139
    current: 908        git     previous: 579

2. Create a VI where two loops run in parallel and share a threshold value.
    threshold: 3
    threshold: 12

3. Create a VI which converts a decimal number to a binary number (displayed in
numeric indicator).
    decimal: 2              binary: 10
    decimal: 22             binary: 10110